proposal.description: Add an entry for the scikit-learn LocallyLinearEmbedding class instantiation, which is used for non-linear dimensionality reduction (manifold learning).
proposal.rationale: This class is a key component for manifold learning, transforming high-dimensional input features into lower-dimensional embeddings. Tracking its configuration (hyperparameters) and instantiation is essential for data provenance, as it significantly alters the input data structure.
